forest.poplar.classes package¶

Submodules¶

forest.poplar.classes.history module¶

This empty module is a placeholder. We anticipate the need for tools to handle longitudinal tracking of categorical variables (e.g. timezones, device power states).

forest.poplar.classes.registry module¶

This empty module is a placeholder for identifier management tools and directory management tools.

forest.poplar.classes.template module¶

This empty module is a placeholder. We anticipate the need for classes that will enable object & data persistence. This module will contain the template(s) for such classes.

forest.poplar.classes.trackers module¶

This empty module is a placeholder. We anticipate the need for tools to handle online calculation of summary statistics, such as an implementation of Welford’s algorithm.
